description: Control shall set Temp_warning_light_EL to ON when Temp_warning_electric of PropulsionController is 1.0.
Control shall set Temp_warning_light_EL to OFF when Temp_warning_electric of PropulsionController is 0.0.
Control shall set Temp_warning_light_TU to ON when Temp_warning_turbine of PropulsionController is 1.0.
Control shall set Temp_warning_light_TU to OFF when Temp_warning_turbine of PropulsionController is 0.0.
Control shall set Chiller_warning_light to ON when Chiller_warning of PropulsionController is 1.0.
Control shall set Chiller_fault_light to ON when Chiller_fault of PropulsionController is 1.0.
Control shall set System of PropulsionControl to 2.0 when (fuel_flow_reference > max_fuel_flow) and (mode of OPERATION is Takeoff).
title: ElectricDriveTrain ON

description: PropulsionController shall set ElectricDriveTrain of ParallelHybridPropulsion to OFF when (Fault_DCAC of DCACcontroller is 1.0) or (Fault_DCDC of DCDCcontroller is 1.0).
title: ParallelHybridPropulsion OFF

description: Control shall set fuel_flow_reference of PropulsionController to k*A when reference of Throttle is A.
title: Fuel Flow

description: Control shall set reference of Throttle to Throttle_Lever_Angle when Input of Control is Cockpit_Controls.
title: Throttle Lever Angle

description: Control shall set reference of Throttle to Autothrust when Input of Control is Automated_Control.
title: Throttle Autothrust

description: Control shall set fuel_flow_reference of PropulsionControl to max_fuel_flow when fuel_flow_reference > max_fuel_flow.
title: Fuel Flow max

description: Control shall set System of PropulsionController to 1.0 when reference of Throttle >0.
title: TurbineDriveTrain ON

description: Auto_control shall set Starter_Motor_status of PropulsionController to DECLUTCH when speed of Gas Turbine Engine > Y.
title: Starter Motor Fuel System

description: Auto_control shall set Ignitor_status of PropulsionController to OFF when speed of Gas Turbine Engine > Y.
title: Ignition Fuel System

description: Auto_control shall set EGT exceedance light of Aircraft to ON when EGT of Gas Turbine Engine> EGT_permissible.
title: Exhaust Gas Temperature

description: Aircraft shall set Input of Control to Automated_Control when AUTOPILOT of aircraft is ON.
title: Autopilot ON

description: Aircraft shall set Input of Control to Cockpit_Controls when AUTOPILOT of aircraft is OFF.
title: Autopilot OFF
